name: My Father Commemorative 911 Oscuro (2011)
additionalNotes:
Unbanded

The My Father Commemorative 911 Blend 343 10th Anniversary will actually have two different wrappers: 9 sticks with Ecuadorian Habano Rosado with a '96 Corojo binder and 11 sticks have Nicaraguan Oscuro Oscuro all fillers are undisclosed. Only 343 boxes of 20 made.  Pre-orders @  http://www.911cigars.com/
